OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fscattered showers, these most frequent
OL,7,Facross the west. Drier across eastern
OL,8,FAngus. Fresh occasionally strong
OL,9,Fwesterly winds, easing this afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,12,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading from
OL,13,Fthe southwest. Rain patchy across the
OL,14,FCentral Belt and the east. Strong
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FRain, occasionally heavy,
OL,18,Fwill spread southeast across all parts
OL,19,Fin the morning. Then drier with a few
OL,20,Fshowers following on in the afternoon.
OL,21,FWindy at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
